&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant Adult Psychiatrist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will have medical and leadership responsibilities for the assessment and management of patients referred to Bracknell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will fulfill the requirements for the Mental Health Act, including carrying out Mental Health Act assessments, acting as the Responsible Clinician for patients on Supervised Community Treatment orders, and preparation of Mental Health Act reports for those patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact Debra Marsden, Head of Services, Bracknell Locality debra.marsden@berkshire.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
